{"tid":2417093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上海迪士尼躁婦上台打人 狂罵演員是豬","createTime":"2021-02-21T14:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T20:33:33.000Z","uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f2abc26b34dae040c1e396031ea141dc58dede2d","tid":2417093,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"近日內地流傳一段影片，一名女子在上海迪士尼劇場內，突然走上台打演員，打完後還狂罵：你這個豬，不配當中國人！<br />\n<br />\n片中見當時台上有數名演員正在表演，突然一名穿長裙戴帽及戴有口罩的女子，走上台追打其中一名演員，打完後還狂罵：你這個豬，不配當中國人！其他演員都被她的舉動嚇至呆立當場。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，現場工作人員勸該女子離場，但該女子卻執意不願離開，最終導致演出要取消。<br />\n<br />\n有現場觀眾指，演出前在大廳裡有段表演，因搞笑目的和劇情需要，出現了脫褲和抽鞭的場景。該女子認為以上2個行為影響了她女兒的正確價值觀，從而引發上台打人一幕。"},{"pid":"564de4d2ac31aea017f0b2a90e82167d40bf00d0","tid":2417093,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T18:09:58.000Z","msg":"等呀媽教你咩先係正確價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f89895d613f9042515e0a0033c7230802abddda","tid":2417093,"uid":32768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T18:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢啲仔女應該係弱智 <br />\n<br />\n咁易被教壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41a523972375880f0f9a24567c0a159f709e144","tid":2417093,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T18:15:14.000Z","msg":"片: <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210221/JOJG6CB3GZC5ZEYFMBYQN2UL6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210221%2FJOJG6CB3GZC5ZEYFMBYQN2UL6I%2F&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=d4ebf590\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210221%2FJOJG6CB3GZC5ZEYFMBYQN2UL6I%2F&h=3a622955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210221/JOJG6CB3GZC5ZEYFMBYQN2UL6I/</a>"},{"pid":"7daa7bc4c6010b9a39ffb92c4a6b34e70606cc12","tid":2417093,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T18:16:38.000Z","msg":"該女子打完演員後，邊走下台邊說：「叫你狂&hellip;&hellip;把自己當中國人，你看那樣子！下次再敢當着大家的面脫褲子、抽鞭子試試看！你個豬！美國人的豬！」"},{"pid":"83b4149f6b60f36db46007c3e34025ddddc59032","tid":2417093,"uid":52760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T18:23:21.000Z","msg":"義和團"},{"pid":"743cecfdfd218be9a01c7ee8a27eeda36e2f3337","tid":2417093,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T19:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連豬"},{"pid":"d7e5b1d8b9540afb3837933cf4e6fce79d017c37","tid":2417093,"uid":19353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T20:33:33.000Z","msg":"咁就應該連迪士尼都唔好入啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}